e 1 VERY 55+ group, or 2-3 50+ groups. <br><br>OK now heres what the 'raid' will consist of:<br><br>There are 6 mobs that have to be killed in 6 locations: Permafrost, Ferrot, Lesser Fay, Emerald jungle, Stonebrunt, and Swamp of no Hope. Having a Druid with/in the raiding party seems essential, just to get to the places required (he can also track for the mobs, otherwise a ranger/bard will have to). All together, it should take under 3 hours, probably 2. Keep in mind i have no idea what the mobs will drop other than the pieces i need for the epics (some totems).<br><br>Now heres the good part, the mobs are lvl 56 'Spirit of ___&quot; depending on the location. they hit for 225, and cannot be slowed, in addition to that, they cast an AE root/snare. If they are not killed, they will stay up for a matter of almost an hour before despawning, and killing unsuspecting passerby's through the duration. <br><br>Any willing/able bodies to kill these big twerps please post, or give tells in game.<br><br>The date I am planning for this is July 31, Wednesday night at 6pm CST kickoff. <p><p><IMG SRC=http://home.swbell.net/lhays/malerin1.jpg><p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/umalerinpryme.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MalerinPryme</A> at: 7/24/02 12:01:05 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/usionach.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sionach</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 103<br> <font color=#0000FF>(7/24/02 12:22:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fallianceraidforumfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=50.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: a series of kills</span><hr size=1> 6p CST is a little early for me, but if I can get hooked up with you when I get home from work (about 6p PDT), I will be there to help.  <!--EZCODE EMOT